## Job.getDependencies() method

Get children job keys if this job is a parent and has children.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
getDependencies(): Promise<{
        processed: {
            [jobKey: string]: string;
        };
        unprocessed: string[];
    }>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;{ processed: { \[jobKey: string\]: string; }; unprocessed: string\[\]; }&gt;
